		{"id":"c3d4e5f60718293a","type":"group","x":1180,"y":-240,"width":380,"height":420,"color":"1","label":"Vision 自监督"},
		{"id":"aa55bb66cc77dd88","type":"text","text":"## 下游迁移\n- Fine-tuning：全参更新\n- Linear probe：冻结主干+小头\n- Prompt/指令/少量增量：LLM常用","x":-200,"y":70,"width":420,"height":110},
		{"id":"5a6b7c8d9e0f1234","type":"file","file":"02模型/自监督预训练/VAE/VAE（Variational Autoencoder）.md","x":460,"y":360,"width":360,"height":140},
		{"id":"6a7b8c9d0e1f2345","type":"file","file":"02模型/自监督预训练/VAE/VQ-VAE（Vector Quantized Variational Autoencoder，向量量化变分自编码器）.md","x":460,"y":520,"width":360,"height":140},
		{"id":"8a9b0c1d2e3f4567","type":"text","text":"## 基础组件\n- AE重建/去噪、异常检测\n- 特征解缠，分离内容与风格\n- 离散潜在/量化：VQ-VAE、Gumbel-Softmax\n- 变分建模：VAE为生成/表征奠基","x":-200,"y":240,"width":340,"height":100},
		{"id":"1a2b3c4d5e6f7081","type":"file","file":"02模型/自监督预训练/自监督基础/Auto-encoder.md","x":-200,"y":360,"width":280,"height":110},
		{"id":"3a4b5c6d7e8f9012","type":"file","file":"02模型/自监督预训练/自监督基础/特征解缠(Feature Disentanglement).md","x":120,"y":360,"width":320,"height":110},
		{"id":"2a3b4c5d6e7f8091","type":"file","file":"02模型/自监督预训练/自监督基础/异常检测Anomaly Detection.md","x":-200,"y":500,"width":280,"height":110},
		{"id":"4a5b6c7d8e9f0123","type":"file","file":"02模型/自监督预训练/自监督基础/离散潜在表示(Discrete Latent Representation).md","x":120,"y":500,"width":320,"height":120},
		{"id":"7a8b9c0d1e2f3456","type":"file","file":"02模型/自监督预训练/VAE/Gumbel-Softmax（Gumbel Softmax）.md","x":460,"y":680,"width":360,"height":100},
		{"id":"9a0b1c2d3e4f5678","type":"text","text":"## 自回归LM（GPT路线上）\n- 预测下一个token，训练/推理一致\n- 强生成与推理能力，少样本泛化佳","x":740,"y":-210,"width":380,"height":110},
		{"id":"3b4c5d6e7f8a9012","type":"text","text":"## 视觉对比（SimCLR/MoCo/BYOL/DINO）\n- 双视角增广，拉近同图/推远异图\n- 依赖增广设计，适合分类/检测迁移","x":1200,"y":-210,"width":340,"height":110},
		{"id":"1b2c3d4e5f6a7890","type":"text","text":"## 去噪Seq2Seq（T5/BART）\n- 输入删改/打乱/span mask，输出原句\n- 统一“输入→输出”格式，天然适配翻译/摘要/问答","x":740,"y":80,"width":380,"height":120},
		{"id":"0a1b2c3d4e5f6789","type":"file","file":"02模型/自监督预训练/BERT（Bidirectional Encoder Representations from Transformers）.md","x":740,"y":-80,"width":380,"height":130},
		{"id":"4b5c6d7e8f9a0123","type":"text","text":"## Masked Image Modeling（MAE/BEiT）\n- 大比例遮挡patch，预测像素或离散token\n- 更少增广，稳定训练，兼容Transformer","x":1200,"y":-80,"width":340,"height":110},
		{"id":"5b6c7d8e9f0a1234","type":"text","text":"## 生成式视角\n- 扩散/GAN等显式生成也可自监督利用无标签\n- 多用于高质量生成，表征迁移次要","x":1200,"y":60,"width":340,"height":110},
		{"id":"6b7c8d9e0f1a2345","type":"file","file":"02模型/自监督预训练/wav2vec1、2.md","x":740,"y":230,"width":360,"height":140},
		{"id":"7b8c9d0e1f2a3456","type":"text","text":"## HuBERT / WavLM / data2vec\n- 聚类成伪标签，再做mask分类或教师-学生目标\n- 增强噪声与说话人鲁棒性，统一语音表征","x":1120,"y":230,"width":420,"height":120},
		{"id":"8b9c0d1e2f3a4567","type":"file","file":"02模型/自监督预训练/Whisper.md","x":740,"y":420,"width":360,"height":140},
		{"id":"c0a1ddee11223344","type":"text","text":"# 自监督预训练\n- 利用未标注数据构造mask/对比/去噪信号获取通用表征或生成力\n- 先预训练，再用少量标注/提示迁移下游任务","x":-200,"y":-210,"width":420,"height":110},
		{"id":"9c0d1e2f3a4b5c6d","type":"text","text":"## 生成式建模\n- 最大化log p(x)或条件概率；自回归/去噪/补全\n- 典型：GPT系列、BART/T5、像素回归式MAE、扩散模型","x":230,"y":-210,"width":300,"height":110},
		{"id":"ab1c2d3e4f5a6b7c","type":"text","text":"## 掩码建模\n- 随机mask部分输入，仅在mask位计算loss\n- 典型：BERT/MLM、MAE/BEiT、wav2vec2的masked预测","x":230,"y":-80,"width":300,"height":110},
		{"id":"bc1d2e3f4a5b6c7d","type":"text","text":"## 对比学习\n- 同源视角相似，负样本远离；InfoNCE/温度τ\n- 典型：SimCLR/MoCo/BYOL/DINO、语义检索对比","x":230,"y":50,"width":300,"height":110},
		{"id":"fa1b2c3d4e5f6789","type":"file","file":"02模型/自监督预训练/Self-supervised Learning Framework.md","x":-200,"y":-80,"width":420,"height":120}
	],
